Package frc.robot

Class RobotSettings

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.RobotSettings
public class RobotSettings
extends java.lang.Object
Here's where the fun happens. Change config files by changing Robot.settingsFile. Make configs using DefaultConfig. If you dont know whats happening here, please see the docs or use intellisense to find what you are looking for
See Also:
DefaultConfig, Robot.settingsFile
